sequenceDiagram
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant EV as Evaluator Agent
    participant MEM as Memory Agent
    participant ACM as AgentCore Memory
    participant AUR as Aurora (pgvector)
    participant PL as Planner Agent (next session)

    Note over EV: End of session - every answer scored
    EV-->>API: AnswerEvaluation[] for the session
    API->>MEM: Aggregate session evaluations
    MEM->>MEM: Tally recurring weaknessTags, update trend (custom logic)
    MEM->>ACM: Write long-term memory (weaknesses, trend)
    MEM->>AUR: Persist MemoryProfile + session metrics

    Note over PL: NEXT session starts later
    PL->>ACM: Read cross-session memory(candidateId)
    ACM-->>PL: Recurring weak areas + semantic recall
    PL->>AUR: Read improvement trend + strong areas
    AUR-->>PL: Trend data
    PL->>PL: Weight next QuestionPlan toward weak areas
    Note over PL: Session 2 gets harder exactly where Session 1 was weak
